snippet.title: Across the Abyss: Voidborn - Gameplay Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Hades meets Vampire survivors in this topdown action game, where you use chain reactions to destroy all your enemies. 

Join H4v1n in helping your elderly crew members and escape from the attacks of the evil Zaibatsu Corporation.

Play now at
pixelhound.itch.io/voidborn

Follow for more news
